snippet.title: Galactic Trader for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

Atari 8-bit
TRS-80


Game description:

Galactic Trader is the 2nd game in the Galactic Saga series.


What I think:

It's basically like Galactic Empire, but more based on trading.
